snippet.title: MainFrames - Release Trailer
snippet.description:
MainFrames is AVAILABLE now on Steam and Nintendo Switch: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1521360/MainFrames/

Dive into the journey of Floppy, a computer program driven to uncover their unknown origins and unlock their true function inside an operating system!
Help them jump across ever-changing PC frames by rearranging program windows and exploiting glitches to create new pathways!

💬A cast of quirky and colorful characters
💡Innovative and challenging platforming puzzles
🎶Micro-chill beats
🎨Stunning retro aesthetic
❔Many secrets to uncover

Time for you to hop into a platforming adventure of self-discovery set inside a computer!
